        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4440792971" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2400986053613894332">Perhaps the author was going for an amusing ode to James Joyce, whom he so often references. What follows is even more obscure and unreadable. Had the story been shrunk to about 20 pages, there would have been some hope for it. As it was, it took itself entirely too seriously for something so unpleasantly useless, offensive, and dull. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


